author: The Hitlist Team
title: When Jacqueline Fernandez wanted to be a nun
text:
During her growing up years, Jacqueline Fernandez didn't even dream of becoming an actress.

Jacqueline Fernandez 
In fact, when she was about 12, she wanted to become a nun.
And look what she's turned to be now. The actress revealed this unknown side of her on the chat show, 'Look Who's Talking', while tracing her Bollywood journey from her forgettable debut flick 'Aladin' (2009) to the big-ticket 'Kick' (2014) with Salman Khan.
Like they say, if you want to make God laugh, tell him about your plans.
